Vanakkam!
It is with immense pleasure that we invite you to our home in Yaalpaanam – a city of vibrant culture, preciously preserved for generations in a world of its own, and now open for you to discover. Your stay with us comes guaranteed with friendly smiles spread across these lands, as a pleasure of the northern charm that gives our peninsula an identity unlike any other on our tropical isle.
In Jaffna, hotels such as ours were among the first to deliver experiences of exotic luxury. And today, as we flourish in the mystique of a long-forgotten region, we are proud to serve you the finest in contemporary Jetwing hospitality, inspired by our legendary northern heritage.
